column1: Arduino to MATLAB PPM Reader; by Gabriel Staples; 3 April 2014

Note: all of the channel PPM values read in by the Arduino are one or more loop iterations old; ex (if we are only preloading the serial buffer with ONE data packet): the PPM values that the Arduino is grabbing this loop will not be read into MATLAB until the next loop; and the PPM values being recorded this loop are the values the Arduino grabbed during the previous loop.
